farmersdelight.advancement.craft_knife=狩獵採集
farmersdelight.advancement.craft_knife.desc=整一把刀從動植物上獲取更多資源。
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_comfort_food=飽肚暖胃！
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_comfort_food.desc=無論幾咁肚餓，碗裏面溫暖嘅食物都能持續為你提供回復效果。
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_nourishing_food=斤両十足！
farmersdelight.advancement.eat_nourishing_food.desc=盤上嘅食物可以讓你喺一段時間之內都感覺唔到飢餓！
farmersdelight.advancement.get_fd_seed=野生作物
farmersdelight.advancement.get_fd_seed.desc=4 種新嘅植物能夠喺野外搵到，佢哋橫跨各種氣候……或者埋藏喺某些地方嘅箱入面。
farmersdelight.advancement.get_ham=荒野屠夫
farmersdelight.advancement.get_ham.desc=用刀喺豬或野豬獸身上獲得火腿。
farmersdelight.advancement.get_mushroom_colony=「菇」息養奸
farmersdelight.advancement.get_mushroom_colony.desc=修剪一棵完整嘅蘑菇菌落。你需要沃土先可以種到出嚟……
farmersdelight.advancement.get_rich_soil=植物養分
farmersdelight.advancement.get_rich_soil.desc=有機堆肥慢慢分解成沃土，使農地更為豐饒！
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_ropelogged_tomato=蕃茄「高」
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_ropelogged_tomato.desc=喺蕃茄藤上掛繩索，等佢生得更高
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_straw=緊握救命草
farmersdelight.advancement.harvest_straw.desc=破壞草、小麥或水稻來收集禾稈草。
farmersdelight.advancement.hit_raider_with_rotten_tomato=躝屍趷路！
farmersdelight.advancement.hit_raider_with_rotten_tomato.desc=向搶掠者掟腐爛蕃茄！
farmersdelight.advancement.master_chef=我要做廚神
farmersdelight.advancement.master_chef.desc=吃勻每道菜餚！
farmersdelight.advancement.obtain_netherite_knife=如果你頂唔順呢個熱廚房……
farmersdelight.advancement.obtain_netherite_knife.desc=用地獄合金為你把刀升級！唔係就快啲離開廚房。
farmersdelight.advancement.place_campfire=營火晚會
farmersdelight.advancement.place_campfire.desc=放置營火並開始燒嘢食
farmersdelight.advancement.place_cooking_pot=餐點上枱！
farmersdelight.advancement.place_cooking_pot.desc=擺低個煲，準備食材！
farmersdelight.advancement.place_feast=大排筵席
farmersdelight.advancement.place_feast.desc=有啲餐點份量夠多，可以叫埋朋友一齊享用！
farmersdelight.advancement.place_organic_compost=高級堆肥
farmersdelight.advancement.place_organic_compost.desc=放置一啲有機堆肥。與陽光、水和蘑菇接觸嘅話，堆肥效果更佳！
farmersdelight.advancement.place_skillet=好熱！
farmersdelight.advancement.place_skillet.desc=潛行並放置平底鑊
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_all_crops=輪耕
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_all_crops.desc=種植所有你搵到嘅農作物，例如蔬菜、水果、蘑菇或根莖類！
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_rice=浸濕對腳
farmersdelight.advancement.plant_rice.desc=喺淺水坑中種植水稻
farmersdelight.advancement.root=農夫樂事
farmersdelight.advancement.root.desc=更有風味嘅世界喺度等緊你！
farmersdelight.advancement.use_cutting_board=小心手指
farmersdelight.advancement.use_cutting_board.desc=喺砧板上用刀切碎一件物品。
farmersdelight.advancement.use_skillet=便攜式廚房
farmersdelight.advancement.use_skillet.desc=有咗平底鑊，你隨時隨地都能夠大展廚藝。用副手揸著食材，然後靠近熱源！
